================================================================================
This archive is a set of softwares modified and used for the evaluation in the
paper "Lightweight Preemptive User-Level Threads" presented in PPoPP '21.
The original pieces of the code are copyrighted based on the license of each
software. The original license files exist in 'argobots/COPYRIGHT' (Argobots),
'bolt/LICENSE.txt' (BOLT), 'chol/LICENSE' (SLATE), 'hpgmg/LICENSE' (HPGMG), and
'lammps/LICENSE' (LAMMPS). The pieces modified for the evaluation in the paper
are copyrighted based on the license below, except the pieces of the code of
LAMMPS modified for the paper, which are copyrighted based on GNU General
Public License version 2 (see 'lammps/LICENSE').
